Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}亲爱的\NHey, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来得正好\NJust in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给我拿杯冷饮  行吗\NGrab me a cold one, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么不叫莎拉・奥尔科特给你拿\NWhy don't you have Sara Alcott get it for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天呐\NOh, my god!
