Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}玛丽  你在干什么\NMary, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}玛丽  玛丽  救救我  把...\NMary! Mary, help me! Get the --
