Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}玛丽  不要\NMary! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}《凶鬼恶灵》  第八季  第六集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}南方风情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}喂喂\NHeads up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在警用扫描仪上听到了一桩案子\NI caught wind of a case on this police scanner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着像是我们的活儿\NSounds like our kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我离开还不到十分钟\NI wasn't even gone 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  那怎么了\NOkay. That matters why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道  迪恩\NI don't know, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}比如  从普兰提斯岛回来你就没跟我说过话\NHow about because you haven't said a word to me since Prentiss Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么着  你就指望我坐在副驾  不说话\NAnd now, what? You want me to shut up and ride shotgun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当什么事都没发生过吗\Nand act like nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你想谈本尼的事吗\NYou want to talk about Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-行  那就说呗  -好啊\N- Fine. Let's talk. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不如说说他是个吸血鬼\NHow about he's a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}多亏了他我才站在这儿\NHe's also the reason I'm topside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而不是在炼狱里做烤肉\Nand not roasting on a spit in purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还想听什么\NAnything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别弄得像我不理解你\NDon't pretend I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你在下面身不由己\NI know you had to do what you had to down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我十分怀疑你理解炼狱的任何事\NI highly doubt you get anything about purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但你已经出来了  本尼却还活着\NBut you're out now, and Benny's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是我的朋友  萨姆\NHe's my friend, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那我的朋友艾米呢  她又怎么了\NAnd what about my friend, Amy? She was what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你杀她的时候可毫不含糊\N'cause you sure as hell didn't have a problem ganking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人总是会变的  不是吗\NWell, I guess people change, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们还把狼人凯特放走了\NWe let that werewolf Kate go, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为她不一样  她...\NShe was different. She --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得本尼也不一样\NYou think Benny's different?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是不是说他不直接吸人血什么的\NDid he tell you he's not drinking live blood or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你居然相信他\NAnd you believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行  你说得对  人是会变\NOkay. You know, you're right. People do change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错  我找了个吸血鬼兄弟\NYeah. I got a vampire buddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而你把电话关了一年\Nand you turn your phone off for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别扯到我身上\NDon't turn this on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  如果本尼犯错了\NLook, Benny slips up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其他猎人干掉了他  那就这样了\Nand some other hunter turns his lights out, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但绝不会是你  对吧\NBut it's not gonna be you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你去不去\NYou coming or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这家伙正在车底下捣鼓\NSo, guy's old lady comes home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他老婆回到家里\Nwhile he's working underneath his ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一脚油门踩到底  削掉了他半个脑袋\Nputs the pedal to the metal, and takes half his head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就这样吗\NWhat, that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}简而言之就是这样\NYeah, in a nutshell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她说她昏过去了  什么都不记得了\NShe says she blacked out, doesn't remember a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听起来像是疯了\NWell, sounds like insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可能吧\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么觉得这是我们的事\NSo, how does that make this our kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}萨姆  因为凯文不见了  行吗\NBecause, Sam, Kevin's in the wind, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就像个逛窑子的太监  闷闷不乐\NYou're sulking around like a eunuch in a whorehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我忍不住问自己\Nand I can't help but ask myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}削脑袋什么时候不是我的事了\Nwhen is decapitation not my thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}联调局\NFBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊  我们恰好就在附近\NYeah, happened to be in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}先是来了个德州骑警  现在又是你们\NFirst a Texas ranger, now you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}德州骑警\NTexas ranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对啊  先生  就在那边\NYes, sir. Right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}逗我玩儿呢\NOh, you got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好啊  查克・诺里斯\NHey, Chuck Norris.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}萨姆  迪恩\NSam? Dean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}忘了他多爱抱人了\NForgot he was a hugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-过来抱抱  -好吧  行啦\N- Come here! - All right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们在处理公务呢\NWe're still -- we're still working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们都不知道我有多想你们\NUh, you guys have no idea how much I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让我们单独待会儿  好吗\NUm, excuse us, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是  我们就过来\NYeah, we'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}德州骑警  盖思  你搞笑呢\NA Texas ranger, Garth? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这可是密苏里\NWe're in Missouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么了\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拜托  我穿着西装就像丧葬承办人\NCome on. I look like a funeral director in one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}先前我听人说你们重出江湖了\NI heard some chatter you two were back in the batter's box,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还不信  现在我信了\Nbut I didn't believe it till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}稍等\NOh, uh, one sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}厄尔  有什么情况\NYo, Earl. What you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个幽灵\NA revenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  你准备一口棺材和几根银钉\NOkay, uh, you'll need a casket and some silver spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有  别被咬到了\NOh, and don't get bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不会害你变异  但会疼死你\NNo, it won't turn you, but it will hurt like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都找到后\NOkay, so, once you got all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把那东西钉在棺材里  埋结实了\Nnail that sucker in, bury him, and throw away the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}知道了吗\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就这样  再见\NAll right. Hasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在干什么\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的工作啊  伙计\NMy job, hombre.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-你的工作  -是啊\N- Your "Job"? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你什么时候干起咨询来了\NAnd since when is giving advice your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等等  你就是那个新鲍比吗\NHold up. Are you the new Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给我闭嘴\NYou shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你也闭嘴\NYou shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真的\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}鲍比没了  你们俩都失踪了\NBobby was gone. You two were M.I.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那段时间很古怪的\NIt was a weird time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}总得有人来接手\NSomebody had to step in and take up the slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好了\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们还是继续工作\NLet's just get back to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过后再来谈这个事情  好吗\Nand we'll talk about this later, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}盖思刚刚是在指挥我们吗\NDid Garth just tell us what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}斯科特・卢\NUh, Scott Lew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这两位先生是联调局的人\NThese gentlemen here are with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}卢先生的父母就是这件...\NMr. Lew's parents were the individuals involved in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不幸事件的当事人\Nunfortunate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}节哀顺变\NSorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有几个问题  卢先生\NJust a few questions, Mr. Lew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你父母会不会  感情出现了什么问题\NUm, by any chance were your parents having... marital problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有  至多就是些小磕绊\NNo. Uh, no more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你母亲的健康状况如何\NWhat about your mother's health?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这会不会是癫痫  中风发作\NAny chance this was a seizure, a stroke,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有什么说得通的解释吗\Nanything that might help explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想没有\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们正在医院给她做检查\NUm, they're checking her out at the, um, hospital right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有什么古怪的表现吗\NWhat about stranger behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}古怪  譬如说\NStranger? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听见幻声  看到幻象...\NHearing voices, seeing things --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你母亲提过这样的事情吗\NYour mother mention anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我父母结婚三十多年了\NMy parents were married for 30 years --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}高中时就是恋人\NHigh-school sweethearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不管你们怎么查\NThere's no good explanation for why this happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这事根本解释不通\Nno matter where you want to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  谢谢你  斯科特\NOkay, well, thank you, Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}保持联系\NWe'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有电磁干扰\NNo EMF.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有硫磺的痕迹\NNo traces of sulfur anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不出所料  白跑了\NLike I thought -- bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别这么着急  萨姆\NHold on there, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有许多需要考虑的因素\NThere's a lot of things to factor in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这事是昨晚发生的\NUh, it happened last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}读不到电磁干扰很正常\Nso the readings could be cold by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说得对\NGood point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}再说了  即使有硫磺\NAnd, uh, even if there was any sulfur,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}[巴尼・法夫是搞笑电视剧中的副警长]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}巴尼・法夫和他的手下\NBarney Fife and his crew
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}恐怕是把犯罪现场\Nprobably contaminated the whole crime scene
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以及所有证据都弄乱了\Nand any evidence that was here with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他还真不赖\NWow. He's on a roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可以这么说\NThat's one word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伙计们  我好像有发现\NUh, guys, I think I found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是口香糖还是灵质\NIs that gum, or is that ectoplasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}灵质一般是黑的吧\NEctoplasm is usually black, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}绝对是灵质\NDefinitely ectoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会是什么呢  应该是鬼魂吧\NSo, what are we thinking -- uh, some kind of ghost, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}麦克雷骑警\NUh, Ranger McCrae here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要是哪只手机铃是锤子乐队的  我就砸了它\NIf one of those things rings Hammer, I'm throwing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}太好了\NOh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢了医生\NThanks, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我嘱咐过法医\NAsked the coroner to drop me a line
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}尸检如果有什么不寻常就通知我\Nin case the autopsy turned up anything... unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们猜怎么着\NAnd guess what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}死者胸口刻着一个词  "奥尔科特"\NOur dead guy had the word "Alcott" carved into his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}用什么刻的\NWith what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}据法医猜测\NCoroner's best guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是他老婆玛丽的指甲\NHis wife Mary's fingernails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}卢太太  能给我们讲讲发生了什么吗\NMrs. Lew, can you tell us what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我当时在商店买杂货\NI was at the store getting groceries,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等我再回过神来\Nand the next thing I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我儿子斯科特发现我在车道上\Nmy son Scott finds me in the driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}切斯特已经...\NAnd Chester was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你对发生的事有任何印象吗\NDo you remember anything at all about what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}切斯特的死\NUm... Chester dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不太记得\NNot really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只有零星的记忆\NBits and pieces, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}比如呢\NSuch as?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我记得他的尖叫\NI remember his screams...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}橡胶灼烧的味道\Nthe smell of burnt rubber, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我记得我非常愤怒\NI remember feeling so angry --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无法抑制的狂怒  我不能自控\Njust uncontrollable rage, like I wasn't myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一切结束之后\NAnd after it was over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那种愤怒\Nall that anger was --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就消失了\NIt was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}夫人  "奥尔科特"这个词你熟悉吗\NUh, ma'am, does the word "Alcott" mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她跟这件事有什么关系\NWhat does she have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是女的\NIt's a she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}高中时我和我丈夫切斯特恋爱了好几年\NMy husband, Chester, and I were going steady in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}感情本来很稳固  却突然大吵一架\Nfor a few years already when we had a big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为什么\NWhat about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是件蠢事\NSomething stupid, I'm sure.
