Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}原来如此\NOh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真让人难过\NSo sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真的跟切斯特约过会吗\NIs it true you and Chester... dated a ways back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}联调局问这种问题可真是奇怪啊  不是吗\NWell, that is an odd question for the FBI, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不会相信我问过多少奇怪的问题\NYou wouldn't believe the awkward questions I've had to ask people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  没错\NWell yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我和老色鬼切斯特一起参加过毕业舞会\NMe and that old tomcat, Chester, we went to prom together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是这样\NThat's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}仅此而已吗\NAnd that's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我算不上是个好女孩\NWell, I wasn't exactly a good girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你是想问这个\Nif that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}打那之后\NAnd after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以为我会和切斯特轰轰烈烈地爱一场\NI-I thought that Chester and I were gonna be hot and heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是有缘无分\NBut it just wasn't meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一星期后  他就跟玛丽就私奔了\NAnd, uh, a week later, he eloped with Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那之后你跟他们还说过话吗\NDid you speak much to Mary or Chester again after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}倒是见过面  野餐之类的\NWell, I'd see them about, you know -- picnics and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:17:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不过  玛丽把他看得很紧\NBut...Mary kept Chester on a pretty short leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说实话  我是翻篇了  可她却没有\NHonestly, I'd moved on, but it seems she never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说这是为什么呢\NAnd why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想在她的心里\NWell, I guess in her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我永远提醒着她切斯特曾经的背叛\NI was a reminder of Chester's betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果没有别的事\NSo, if that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  非常感谢你的帮助\NYes, uh, thank you very much for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很久没有让自己如此随性了\NIt's been a long time since I let myself go like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我完全理解\NYeah, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你问我是不是失去了谁\NYou asked me if I lost someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的丈夫\NMy husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}八个月前他在阿富汗牺牲了\NHe died in Afghanistan eight months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这一定很...\NThat must have been, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我无法想象\NI can't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们本可以长相厮守\NWe were together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}至少我以为会那样\NOr at least it seemed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后有一天  唐突然参军了\NThen one day, Don just enlists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都没问我的意见\NDidn't ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只说他想去做该做的事情\Njust said something about wanting to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后他就远渡重洋  留我孤身一人\NNext thing I know, he's off overseas and I'm all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只有他的信和电话\NI got a couple letters, some phone calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}再就是军队上门通报死讯\Nand then a knock at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就这样\NJust like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我所到之处\NAnd everywhere I looked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都是人们的议论和同情\Nall I could see was judgment and pity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一切一切都让我想起唐\Nand just this constant reminder of Don everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我搬到了这里\NSo I moved here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我却越来越糟\N...and became even more of a hot mess than I already was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直到你撞了条狗\NAnd you hit a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}松手  小子\NEasy there, flyweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上次你乱喝酒\NLast time you drank a beer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人都粘在地板上了\NI had to pick you up off the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}参见S07E18
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真是个白痴\NYou're such an idjit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}白痴是生气时用来骂人的话\NIdjit's supposed to be used angrily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}懂吗  我不爱听\NOkay? Not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不会用就别说\NIf you're gonna butcher it, don't say it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NWhoa, then. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}虽然不关我的事\NN-none of my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但这是因为你跟萨姆的事吗\Nbut...this have anything to do with you and...Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说得对  这不关你的事\NNo, you had it right. It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是觉得\NIt just seems that you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们之间的关系有点紧张\Nare a little tense around each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们很好\NWe're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可以继续工作了吗\NCan we get back to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就想告诉你\NJust, uh -- just letting you know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可以为你们做任何事\Nthat I'm here for you, for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道有时候  鲍比会...\NI know sometimes Bobby, he would --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不是鲍比\NYou're not Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}懂吗\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你永远不会成为鲍比  所以别闹了\NYou're never gonna be Bobby, so stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}鲍比是我们大家的朋友  不仅属于你和萨姆\NBobby belonged to all of us, Dean -- not just you and Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是用他教我的东西\NNow, I'm just taking what he showed me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}想要造福他人  仅此而已\Nand trying do something with it. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你看看能不能在他那本破书里\NWhy don't you see if you can find something
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}找到什么有用的\Nin that bourbon-drenched book of his
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们也好早日离开南部\Nso we can get the hell out of Dixie, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好  我看着呢\NYeah. I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}苏塞克斯不是"谁"  而是"什么"\N"Sussex" is not a who, it's a what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是一家一年前才倒闭的公司\NIt's a business that went belly-up about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看这里\NLook at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个被斯科特爆头的家伙\NSo, the guy that Scott brained?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是他以前的合伙人  把公司搞破产了\NHis old business partner -- ran the company into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}斯科特和杰夫是有矛盾的\NSo, Scott had a beef with Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看来是这样\NLooks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我开扬声器了\NHey, you're on speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉・奥尔科特没问题\NSara Alcott's clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她只不过是\Nif you look past the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟切斯特在舞会之夜有一夜情罢了\Nshe and Chester knocked boots on prom night back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  那么...\NOkay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}玛丽对莎拉怀恨在心\NMary has a grudge against Sara,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而斯科特对杰夫怀恨在心\Nand Scott has a grudge against Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些线索除了让我头疼\NBesides the fact this is making my head hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟鬼魂能扯上什么关系\Nhow does this add up to a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伙计们\NGuys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}鲍比在这儿写了\NBobby has it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}绿色粘液代表厉鬼的存在\NGreen goo equals a spectre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也就是鬼魂吧\NWhich equals ghost, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  算是吧\NMm, yeah, kind of.
