Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.66,0:28:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你走的时候记得锁门\NUh, just lock up when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.90,0:28:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我迟到了\NI'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.13,0:28:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等等  什么\NWait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.23,0:28:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是觉得我俩最好别产生什么误会\NI just think it's better if neither of us get the wrong idea here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.49,0:28:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好啊\NO-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.13,0:28:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我昨晚说了很多话\NAnd I know I said a lot of things last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.16,0:28:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道没办法叫你忘记\Nand I know I can't ask you to forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.60,0:28:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是  忘了吧\NBut just...do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.45,0:28:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.30,0:28:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为我不需要你的同情\NBecause I don't need your pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.10,0:28:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不需要你也对我流露其他人的那种...\NI don't need you looking at me the way they all --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.87,0:28:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就那种眼神\Nlike that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.62,0:28:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得我是同情你吗\NWait, um you think this is pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.61,0:28:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}艾米利亚  我很高兴你告诉我唐的事\NAmelia, I'm glad you told me about Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.08,0:28:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这让我能理解你\NIt helps me understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.14,0:28:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}理解我的生活有多糟吗  你以为我不知道\NHow messed up I am? You think I don't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.89,0:28:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你用不着同情我  萨姆\NYou don't have to feel sorry for me, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.37,0:28:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是那个意思\NI didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.60,0:28:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行了  我快迟到了  那么...\NYeah, well, like I said, I'm late. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.74,0:29:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}喂  你来不来\NHey, you comin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.49,0:29:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们知道称他为"无名"战士是有原因的吧\NYou do know there is a good reason he's called the unknown soldier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.29,0:29:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  我们想查查这么些年来\NRight. Uh, we were just hoping maybe a theory or two
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.54,0:29:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会不会有什么说法\Nhad been a floated around over the years --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.48,0:29:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当地的传闻\NSomething local, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.50,0:29:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}确实有\NThere is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.44,0:29:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}裁判\NHey, Ump.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.57,0:29:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}记得我吗  你判我盗二垒\NYou remember me? I stole second!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.54,0:29:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}卡尔  你这是做什么\NKarl? What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.74,0:29:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么要...\NWhy are you doing --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.38,0:29:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么要用你的脑干做芥末酱吗\NWhy am I gonna make mustard from your brain stem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.01,0:29:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.55,0:29:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么罚我出局  裁判\NWhy did you call me out, Ump?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.15,0:29:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.45,0:29:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.38,0:29:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看来是没子弹了\NLooks like you're shooting blanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.84,0:30:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好痒啊\NHey, that tickled.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.01,0:30:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}联邦军的柯林斯下士\NCorporal Collins of the union
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.68,0:30:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}射杀了他加入了邦联的兄弟万斯\Nshot and killed his brother, Vance, who fought for the confederacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.31,0:30:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本地的小伙子\NLocal boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.48,0:30:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是说两兄弟在内战时是敌对双方\NWait, so two brothers fought on opposite sides of the Civil War?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.51,0:30:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}据说万斯死前起誓要找兄弟报仇\NLegend has it that Vance swore vengeance on his brother with his dying breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.34,0:30:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}多年后  无疑是因良心不安\NYears later -- consumed by guilt, no doubt --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.69,0:30:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}下士从他当年埋兄的\Nthe Corporal dug his brother up
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.47,0:30:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}战场上把尸体挖了出来\Nwhere he'd buried him on the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.88,0:30:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}带回了家\Nand brought him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.66,0:30:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是说这个万斯就是无名战士\NAre you suggesting this Vance guy is the unknown soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.90,0:30:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有这种说法\NThat's one theory, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.58,0:30:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是什么\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.14,0:30:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}卡尔  听着\NKarl, listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.23,0:30:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道是厉鬼让你发火\NI know the spectre's turning the temperature up in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.58,0:30:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉我通灵物件是什么\NSo just tell me what the object is,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.54,0:30:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们把这个捣蛋鬼送回去\Nand we'll send this joker home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.39,0:30:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可不这样想\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.94,0:30:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}托你的福  事情还没完呢\NThere's unfinished business, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.55,0:30:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}厉鬼喜欢你\NOh, the spectre likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.59,0:30:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是吗\NOh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.63,0:30:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不如你让他出来\NWhy don't you tell him to come on out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.77,0:31:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们做对儿情侣镯\NWe'll make promise bracelets.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.45,0:31:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}大多数士兵都是穷苦农民\NMost of the soldiers were poor farmers,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.92,0:31:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}家人会用绳子穿一分钱给他们\Nso the families would give them a penny on a string.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.27,0:31:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}1859年  印第安人头像硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.91,0:31:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}算是护身符  而且万一迷路了\NIt was for good luck, and in case they ever got lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.65,0:31:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有一分钱买吃的喝的\Nthey always had a penny for food or drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.35,0:31:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一分钱\NA penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.56,0:31:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拿去  试试吧\NHere. Have a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.09,0:31:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是我  留言吧\NIt's me. Do what you gotta.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.10,0:31:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩\NDean, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.78,0:31:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}墓地的地上有根绳子\NThere was a string on the floor of the tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.10,0:31:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}原本穿着一枚硬币\NIt used to hold an old penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.83,0:31:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那就是通灵物件\NThat's the object.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.12,0:31:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们这就过来\NWe're coming right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.57,0:31:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩  怎么回事\NDean? What the hell, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.11,0:31:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们去了医院  你不接电话\NWe went to the hospital. You're not answering your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.72,0:31:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在炼狱的时候你本该去找我\NYou should have looked for me when I was in purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.85,0:32:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}三天前
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.99,0:33:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}清醒点  迪恩\NCome on, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.41,0:33:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道这不是你\NI know it's not you in there pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.96,0:33:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}闭嘴\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.49,0:33:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别动\NDon't!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.38,0:33:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你根本就不想要这种生活\NYou never even wanted this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.31,0:33:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你总是怪我又拉你下水\NAlways blamed me for pulling you back into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.94,0:33:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-不是这样  -真的吗\N- That's not true. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.03,0:33:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}自从你跟我上了路\N'cause everything you've ever done
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.01,0:33:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你做的每件事都是欺骗我\Nsince you climbed into my ride has been to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.66,0:33:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你想要我说什么\NWhat do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.79,0:33:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说我有错吗\NThat I've made mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.28,0:33:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是有错  迪恩\NI've made mistakes, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.18,0:34:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他已经不是迪恩了  萨姆\NThat's not Dean, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.23,0:34:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}闭嘴\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.53,0:34:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有错\NMistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.70,0:34:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那我们就来细数一下小萨姆的伟大功绩\NWell, let's go through some of Sammy's greatest hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.86,0:34:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}饮恶魔血\NDrinking demon blood, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.74,0:34:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}与露比合谋\NBeing in cahoots with Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.14,0:34:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}瞒着我你没了灵魂的事\NNot telling me that you lost your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.89,0:34:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还跟随萨穆埃尔一整年\NOr how about running around with Samuel for a whole year,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.41,0:34:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就让我以为你死了\Nletting me think that you were dead
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.58,0:34:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而你却在为所欲为\Nwhile you're doing all kinds of crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.98,0:34:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些不叫有错  萨姆\NThose aren't mistakes, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.10,0:34:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而是选择\NThose are choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.23,0:34:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行  你说得对\NAll right. You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.65,0:34:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们俩都有点轻率了\NWe've both played a little fast and loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.16,0:34:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  我也许会撒谎  但绝不曾背叛你\NYeah, I might have lied, but I never once betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.99,0:34:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}绝不曾不管你的死活\NI never once left you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.26,0:34:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为了什么  一个姑娘\NAnd for what, a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.89,0:34:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为了个姑娘扔下我不管\NYou left me to die for a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.63,0:35:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}盖思  不要\NGarth, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.93,0:35:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别担心  他不会杀了我的\NNo, he won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.07,0:35:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他怨念的不是我\NHis beef isn't with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.74,0:35:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不会朝我开枪的对吗  迪恩\NYou're not gonna shoot me, are you, Dean?
