Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.26,0:39:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我们不需要同情\Nbut we're not to be pitied.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.45,0:39:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}几个月前我失去了哥哥  迪恩\NLook, I lost my brother, Dean, a few months ago.
