Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.36,0:39:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我开始同情你了\Nsee, now I pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.67,0:39:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其实  我倒不是这个意思\NOh, look, I mean, that wasn't really my point.
