Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们在德克萨斯州的科米特有个住处\NShe and I had a place together in Kermit, Texas.
